Package: FastStack
Type: Package
Title: Haplotype Block Discovery and localGEBV Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Will", "Shaffer",
      email = "w.shaffer@uq.edu.au",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools to order marker maps, compute pairwise linkage
    disequilibrium, define haplotype blocks, estimate local genomic estimated
    breeding values (localGEBV), visualize marker and haplotype patterns,
    and optimize parent selection with a genetic algorithm workflow.
